Let A = \{1,2,3,4,5\}\text{,} B = \{3,4,5,6,7\}\text{,} and C = \{2,3,5\}\text{.}




Find A \cap B\text{.}






Find A \cup B\text{.}






Find A \setminus B\text{.}






Find A \cap \overline{(B \cup C)}\text{.}

