BEGIN_PGML Consider the function [`f:\{1,2,3,4\} \to \{1,2,3,4\}`] given by
[```\newcommand{\twoline}[2]{\begin{pmatrix}#1 \\ #2 \end{pmatrix}}\newcommand{\amp}{&} f(n) = \twoline{1 \amp 2 \amp 3 \amp 4}{4 \amp 1 \amp 3 \amp 4} \text{.}```]
